Dataset Files Description:-

1. data_set_ALL_AML_train.csv
Contains training gene expression measurements from leukemia patient samples.

2. data_set_ALL_AML_independent.csv
Contains independent patient samples used for testing and expanded evaluation.

3. actual.csv
Contains leukemia labels (ALL/AML) corresponding to patient samples.

Dataset Source:
Golub Leukemia Gene Expression Dataset (1999) - Kaggle
The following code will download the dataset in your terminal.
  
  import kagglehub
  # Download latest version
  path = kagglehub.dataset_download("crawford/gene-expression")
  print("Path to dataset files:", path)
  

Description:
The dataset contains gene expression values collected using microarray experiments for leukemia subtype classification.
